ns of the dust-torus model. Here the recent discovery of the 10mic\nsilicate feature in emission in luminous quasar spectra is reported.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2005 08:48:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
