is of a DSR Minkowski limit, there is\nan additional challenge for those in the quantum-gravity community attributing\nto the Planck length the role of \"fundamental length scale\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jun 2005 20:03:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
